==============
 JSONResolver
==============

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/inveniosoftware/jsonresolver.svg
        :target: https://travis-ci.org/inveniosoftware/jsonresolver

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/coveralls/inveniosoftware/jsonresolver.svg
